sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Task A
    participant B as Task B
    participant P as Pool 0.3.0
    participant C1 as Conn 1
    participant C2 as Conn 2

    A->>P: lease
    P->>C1: open
    P-->>A: conn 1
    A->>C1: stream active
    B->>P: lease
    P->>C2: open
    P-->>B: separate conn 2
    B->>C2: stream active
